title: Top O' The MornTrend 9/13: YouTube Kids, Britney Spears, Disney Store, MTV VMA, Amy Coney Barret, CA Recall, Rental Cars
itunes:title: Top O' The MornTrend 9/13: YouTube Kids, Britney Spears, Disney Store, MTV VMA, Amy Coney Barret, CA Recall, Rental Cars
description:
In this edition of Top O' The MornTrend, Jack and Miles discuss YouTube corrupting the youth, Britney Spears getting engaged (hopefully with a prenup), the Disney Store moving to Target, the VMAs happening, Amy Coney Barrett's weird speech, Rose McGowan supporting Larry Elder in the CA recall, and car rentals being hard to come by.
